Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新聞的傳播勢不可擋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:03.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:07.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.31,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}精神勝利大法好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:13.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}本想跟著節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.32,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}搖擺搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但外面也太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}噪音·消除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:27.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是用手指轉個圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你的選擇是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 憋紅了臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}準備唾棄的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:41.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}興趣的不同 信仰的不一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}讓你感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但決定我前行方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:51.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}僅僅是喜歡還是討厭
